Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:07.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女孩是什麼顏色 男孩又是什麽顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:12.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女孩是紅色 男孩是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:14.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:19.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}某種顏色的女孩和某種顏色的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:24.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果邂逅 那在他們之間會產生什麼顏色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定 還是純白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:30.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如同新展開的畫布一般純潔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:32.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在未來才能決定顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:37.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那戀愛的顏色一定是白色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.15,0:00:44.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能將兩人的顏色染上的透徹的純粹的白色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:37.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}純白色的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:35.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 果然還是迷路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我又犯老毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:43.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在連自己在什麼地方都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 迷路還是好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:48.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃那麼漂亮 我一直都很擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:53.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用擔心的 迷路的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:56.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你迷路的話 只要我能找到就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:03:01.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 迷路的話只要讓哥哥找到就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:06.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 能照到那附近的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起來沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:42.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:52.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是是舊市街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}莫非那裡有各務賣場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:01.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:07.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:32.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:45.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 現在在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:53.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:56.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}離開剛才的地方了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:05:00.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 被一隻奇怪的生物所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:08.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要再到處走了 會讓我找不著的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:12.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我知道了 我不再到處亂走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}（請給電池充電）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:19.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電池沒電了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 附近有沒有什麼標誌物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:31.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直都是圍墻 還有就是能看到山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:32.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結女的山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會馬上找到你的 等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我不會亂走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放心 我馬上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:31.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎回來 你到底去了什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}金木樨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下雨了 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:47.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我答應哥哥不到處亂走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:08:00.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}您所撥打的電話不在服務區或已關機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:20.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 瓜生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:27.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生新吾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:31.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 是的 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:34.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 聯繫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:39.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你 是你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下雨沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:55.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事 愛理和我一起撐著傘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:59.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 是誰 剛才的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 愛理的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:01.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:03.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那這個手機是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:04.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:07.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 櫻乃 那你現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:08.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:10.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:11.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}換我接電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫瀨名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}重新正式問候一下 我叫瓜生新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:21.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真對不起 我妹妹給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:28.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實我也迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:34.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}心裡也有些不安 反而是櫻乃幫了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:38.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 你要是道謝 我也會不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:41.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}兩個人都還迷著路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:43.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也是路痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:49.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才的 可不是值得笑的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 從那裡能看到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:59.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡是上坡的路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}遠遠可以看到街市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:06.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那條路的相反方向 是朝著山裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}朝著山一直向前走的話 應該可以到公園的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:15.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 哥哥現在在什麼地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:16.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也在舊市街
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在公園的西門附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:24.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 進公園以後的路 我也清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:41.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:45.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 再過一會就能見到哥哥了 再加油一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:49.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:55.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 連哥哥也這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過說得也是 一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:13.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是櫻乃的哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:19.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:28.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 真的萬分的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 反而是我得到了很多幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:36.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還想再見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:46.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是 因為 我們已經是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:11:59.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:02.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 熱水馬上就要燒好了 先進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:12.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}差點就要得感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:27.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天開始就是十月了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:38.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也來洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我在裡面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事 我們是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可能沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:52.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被雨淋濕 身體冰涼的兄妹 在一起取暖...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爸爸和媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像接下來的一段時間會很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:35.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:36.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}猜對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:41.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}各務賣場的魚店 有打折的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:44.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就是昨天的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真正要買的是這個才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:48.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:54.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天是第一天 不能給哥哥隨便的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:11.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}琳琅滿目昂貴商品的各務賣場 和平常的我們完全無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:23.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 路痴的櫻乃冒著迷路的危險 到那裡去購物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:27.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}全都是為了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:40.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃冬天的校服 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:43.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}4個月沒見了吧 哥哥的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的就沒什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 櫻乃穿這衣服很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 準太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:02.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 是新吾啊 還有櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:03.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就讓我們出發去新學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}少女和她的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來我們就要踏上的路就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:20.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不錯呢 這樣可疑的舉止 我都燃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:27.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是被櫻乃給丟下了 新吾你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:36.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 聽說準太有婚約者了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 真尖銳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好的吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和女... 女生們的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:08.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得 好像有些要窒息一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那句話 我的立場怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:17.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們的母校 在新市街的各務台學園
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為陷入經營困境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:22.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在結姬女子學園的提議下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}進行了學校合併
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 說起舊市街的結女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結姬女子學園是歷史悠長的大小姐學校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:38.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從十月份開始在那裡實驗性地 將一年級二年級選拔出來的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:41.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為試驗生就讀結女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:46.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯 我和櫻乃 還有準人都是其中的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:51.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:53.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}名門女校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:58.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:04.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼疑問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:11.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:18.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔從初次見面的人 得到我回來了的答覆還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:19.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:23.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}您一定很能幹吧 安潔莉娜大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:27.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}莫非您是華族或者貴族的後代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:30.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯 您的英姿依稀散髮出高貴的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:36.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能讓我心這樣砰砰直跳的 好久都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:39.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的是很紳士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔都陶醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結女的歡迎Neta吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:51.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得因太過吃驚而逃跑的人也會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:55.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個不用擔心 我會帶好路的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:59.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那你是 結女的女僕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:02.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是 教工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:06.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不不 雖然讓我來負責帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我安潔 是野生女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:10.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}野生?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:11.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女僕?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:13.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}野生女僕?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:21.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的名字是安潔莉娜·菜夏·史威爾 以後我們就認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:23.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:27.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們是暫時來上學的試驗生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:32.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在就帶你們去講堂 請移步這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:43.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過這真的是華麗的校舍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:47.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒想到還是野生女僕出沒的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:52.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過連野生女僕都遇到了 應該不會有更值得驚訝的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:15.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個生物 好像在哪裡見過一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:17.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:27.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 椋梨 瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好厲害啊 大小姐學校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:35.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 這裡也像是能舉辦舞會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:39.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然出現女僕來迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:43.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}萬智老師 上去說幾句話比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:48.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}振作一點 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:51.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是… 年輕的男性有那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:54.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是結女的老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}集合場所在這裡就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:06.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 那個… 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:08.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}萬智老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:17.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學園長馬上就要來了 再稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:20.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:22.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好痛… 很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是一直都這麼強勢 會不受歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:31.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別囉嗦了 這樣會讓各務台的學生等很久的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:32.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:33.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我把學園長帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:39.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}八冢老師也振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:47.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 真的是太頑固了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:48.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道是生理中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼呀 因為宿醉讓他人久等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:56.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是母親提出的建議呢 學園合併
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:21:00.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎 我一直覺得是這樣的 你是很歡迎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才沒有歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然是愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:04.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:09.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 您們曾經謀面過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:14.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名 是結女的學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理 又見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼 是愛理認識的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡是我們的學園
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論學園長是如何決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:43.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但決不是所有的學生都贊同合併的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:48.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至少我就 不歡迎你們男生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:52.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為這個結姬女子學園 是女校!

Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:39.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等 瓜生 你到底在看什麼地方呢
